@startuml
actor App 
box "Runtime"
participant Orchestrator
database GlobalNode
database LocalNodes
end box

App -[#green]> Orchestrator: Request:\nAlgorithm list, data,\nfilters, transformation
Orchestrator -[#blue]-> Orchestrator: Control:\nRun Algorithm 1
ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode : Algorithm 1
GlobalNode -[#red]> LocalNodes: Transfer:\nResult of Algorithm 1
LocalNodes -[#red]> LocalNodes: Transform:\nCreate new table from \nAlgorithm 1 result and local data
Orchestrator -[#blue]-> Orchestrator: Control:\nRun Algorithm 2
ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode : Algorithm 2
GlobalNode -[#red]> LocalNodes: Transfer:\nResult of Algorithm 2
LocalNodes -[#red]> LocalNodes: Transform:\nCreate new table from \nAlgorithm 2 result and local data
... Repeat ...
Orchestrator -[#green]> App: Response:\nFinal result
@enduml


